For the Genes and Evolution course, you need to download the program MEGA.
Choose your operating system (Windows, Mac, Linux) here: https://www.megasoftware.net

All newer Macs (older than 2016) are 64bit. 

Check to see if your windows needs 64 or 32 bit by:
Windows 10 and Windows 8.1
  Select the Start  button, then select Settings > System > About .
    Open About settings
     At the right, under Device specifications, see System type.
Windows 7
  Select the Start button , right-click Computer, and then select Properties.
    Under System, see the system type.

